mockoon-cliw - Mockoon CLI Wrapper

USAGE:
    mockoon-cliw [--port=port] [--data=requests] [-d=requests]

DESCRIPTION:
    Mockoon CLI wrapper that starts mock server with monitoring
    and notification capabilities.

OPTIONS:
    --port=port
        Port to run mock server on

    --data=requests | -d=requests
        JSON requests file to serve

CONFIGURATION:
    -mockoon-requests FILE
        Default JSON requests file

EXAMPLES:
    mockoon-cliw --port=3000 --data=api.json
    mockoon-cliw -d=mock-data.json
